description: The image is a flyer or informational graphic for a session titled "Maximizing iOS Potential: Understanding SKAN / AAK for User Acquisition and Re-engagement". The session is scheduled from 9:30 am to 10:00 am. The speakers are Justin Warshavsky (Draftkings), Sandy Shen (LinkedIn), Zach Gryphon (Wavemaker) and Mark Menery (Dataseat). The location is Boulevard Ballroom 159-163, Main. The session sponsor is the MAU Vegas Show Team, presented by AppsFlyer. There is a yellow calendar icon on the right.
